# S1-G0 · I5 — Code owners.
#
# Fiscal is compliance-critical: the platform is never the fiscal issuer
# (ADR-0006), and fiscal changes carry legal risk. Any PR touching packs/fiscal/
# requires review from a fiscal code owner. Enforced by branch protection
# ("Require review from Code Owners") on the remote.
#
# NOTE (solo owner): while @eduardovrocha is the only owner, GitHub will not let
# them approve their own PR — so "require Code Owner review" blocks self-merge.
# That is the intended friction (fiscal needs a second set of eyes); until there
# is a second reviewer, either add one to a fiscal-reviewers team and point the
# rules at it, or keep require_code_owner_reviews off in protect-main.sh.

# Default owner for everything.
*                       @eduardovrocha

# Fiscal pack — designated reviewer(s).
/packs/fiscal/          @eduardovrocha

# Fiscal compliance issue template travels with the fiscal owner too.
/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/fiscal-compliance.yml  @eduardovrocha
